"Personal information can be inferred from the location data recorded with pictures taken with a camera. Exercise caution when posting images to the Internet or other locations where they can be viewed by third parties. In addition, some countries restrict the use of location data systems; before travelling, check with your travel agent or the embassy or tourism board of the country you will be visiting."
